t: 20px;"><em>The U.S. health care system tends to believe that inventing b=
rand new gadgets is the answer to everything. The result is that we try to =
solve problems by building faster and more expensive Ferraris when what we =
really need are better roads.</em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: #4040=
40; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>(5)</s=
